1
00:00:12,380 --> 00:00:18,540
♪My heart flipped when a dynamic
flashed between us someday♪

2
00:00:19,020 --> 00:00:20,380
♪Guided by instinct♪

3
00:00:20,540 --> 00:00:24,660
♪We feel the same reason,
harboring a special feeling underneath♪

4
00:00:24,860 --> 00:00:27,780
♪Amidst the ecstatic shock♪

5
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:30,900
♪I begin to doubt what I see♪

6
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:36,380
♪I can't believe you made me compromise♪

7
00:00:37,060 --> 00:00:40,100
♪The world you're sick of♪

8
00:00:40,420 --> 00:00:43,060
♪I look into it thoroughly♪

9
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:45,340
♪How lucky I am to console you♪

10
00:00:45,540 --> 00:00:48,940
♪When you suffer alone♪

11
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:54,940
♪Yet I realize♪

12
00:00:55,180 --> 00:01:00,100
♪I cannot let go
of the love I hold onto tightly♪

13
00:01:00,300 --> 00:01:03,300
♪As I venture into the world
from a mundane life♪

14
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:06,980
♪You show up at the exact moment♪

15
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:09,740
♪My ambition♪

16
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:12,420
♪Puts an end to this aimless journey♪

17
00:01:12,620 --> 00:01:15,580
♪The familiar light of pursuit
shines into my heart♪

18
00:01:15,820 --> 00:01:18,660
♪From the starting point♪

19
00:01:36,420 --> 00:01:41,380
[South Wind Knows]

20
00:01:41,380 --> 00:01:45,420
[Episode 29]

21
00:01:55,140 --> 00:01:55,820
Coming.

22
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:08,380
These are all Meng's favorites.

23
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:10,780
Dr. Zhu packed them up

24
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:12,180
and asked me to send them over.

25
00:02:15,420 --> 00:02:16,020
Come in.

26
00:02:19,660 --> 00:02:21,020
Is Mr. Meng not at home?

27
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:22,020
He went out.

28
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:32,540
When will he be back?

29
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:33,780
I don't know.

30
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:38,700
You're here for the lawsuit, aren't you?

31
00:02:39,820 --> 00:02:40,580
Please leave.

32
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:42,300
We won't withdraw the lawsuit.

33
00:02:45,260 --> 00:02:46,060
Mrs. Meng.

34
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:50,260
Others might not know,
but you're well aware

35
00:02:51,220 --> 00:02:53,300
that Dr. Zhu cares very much about Meng.

36
00:02:54,820 --> 00:02:56,900
She wouldn't be so careless
to use the wrong drug.

37
00:02:57,260 --> 00:02:58,580
Everyone makes mistakes.

38
00:03:04,420 --> 00:03:06,460
The detailed medical record
is sent to you.

39
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:09,300
You can check on it closely.

40
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,340
That's provided by the hospital.

41
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:12,780
No one knows the genuineness
of the record.

42
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:15,820
Someone told you about this, right?

43
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:18,060
Who are they?

44
00:03:22,420 --> 00:03:23,140
Please leave.

45
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:27,580
Mrs. Meng.

46
00:03:28,900 --> 00:03:30,580
Someone is using your grief

47
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:32,020
to mislead you.

48
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:33,620
No one is misleading us.

49
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:36,180
We insist on seeking justice
for ourselves.

50
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:37,260
Are you aware

51
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:39,660
of how much money and effort
you need to invest in the lawsuit?

52
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:42,260
The lawyer, Mr. Wang, you hired

53
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:43,580
required an expensive fee.

54
00:03:44,540 --> 00:03:46,220
If this lawsuit fails,

55
00:03:46,940 --> 00:03:48,740
the legal fee can be costly.

56
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:50,380
Mr. Wang is a legal aid lawyer.

57
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:51,700
It's free of charge.

58
00:03:57,060 --> 00:03:58,820
The person behind you
told you about this, right?

59
00:04:12,660 --> 00:04:14,020
You can go and ask around.

60
00:04:14,020 --> 00:04:15,620
[Wang Zhiwei, Senior Lawyer]

61
00:04:15,620 --> 00:04:17,260
He's not a legal aid lawyer.

62
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:20,420
Calm down and take a second.

63
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:26,660
What are you doing here?

64
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:27,620
Get out!

65
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,020
Don't you hear me?

66
00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:32,020
Get out of here!

67
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:39,180
Mr. Meng.

68
00:04:40,340 --> 00:04:42,380
I know you've been very busy lately,

69
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:44,540
and you don't have time

70
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:46,180
to hold a proper funeral for Meng.

71
00:04:46,860 --> 00:04:48,220
If you need anything,

72
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:50,060
feel free to give me a call.

73
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:51,460
I'm leaving.

74
00:04:53,340 --> 00:04:54,420
Are you in your right mind?

75
00:04:54,780 --> 00:04:56,140
Why did you open the door?

76
00:05:37,620 --> 00:05:38,140
Mom.

77
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:44,340
Mom.

78
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:47,420
I recorded

79
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:49,500
the conversation that day.

80
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:54,140
What did you just say?

81
00:05:54,820 --> 00:05:55,620
What conversation?

82
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:59,300
About the lawyer.

83
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:01,620
I've given Yunshen that recording.

84
00:06:02,180 --> 00:06:02,980
He's going to use it

85
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:04,460
to prove Dr. Zhu's innocence.

86
00:06:05,420 --> 00:06:06,060
Mom.

87
00:06:06,860 --> 00:06:08,020
Please withdraw the lawsuit.

88
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:09,180
Okay?

89
00:06:09,780 --> 00:06:10,300
You...

90
00:06:15,580 --> 00:06:16,740
You're not my daughter!

91
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:18,380
Mom.

92
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:20,740
Mom.

93
00:06:22,580 --> 00:06:24,140
I know you did this for my own good.

94
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:25,620
But Mom,

95
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:28,260
I don't want to keep Yunshen with me
with this method.

96
00:06:28,820 --> 00:06:30,700
That's not the right way
for someone I love.

97
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:34,100
If you...

98
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:38,660
If you undermined yourself
because of me,

99
00:06:39,780 --> 00:06:40,860
I'll be devastated.

100
00:06:41,460 --> 00:06:42,540
I'll beat myself up.

101
00:06:59,180 --> 00:06:59,820
Mom.

102
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:01,860
I promise you.

103
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:03,980
I'll do anything you say.

104
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:10,700
I'll forget about Yunshen.

105
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:13,020
I promise you

106
00:07:13,980 --> 00:07:15,140
I'll go on blind dates.

107
00:07:22,540 --> 00:07:23,620
Why do I have a disappointing daughter

108
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,780
like you?

109
00:07:41,100 --> 00:07:41,740
Who's this?

110
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:42,900
Mr. Wang.

111
00:07:45,300 --> 00:07:46,140
Mr. Wang.

112
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:48,540
Any progress on the case?

113
00:07:49,220 --> 00:07:49,740
No.

114
00:07:49,980 --> 00:07:50,740
I'm sorry.

115
00:07:51,340 --> 00:07:53,180
I can't help you with the case anymore.

116
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:54,460
Why not?

117
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,060
The evidence is insufficient.

118
00:07:56,180 --> 00:07:56,940
It's hard to continue the lawsuit.

119
00:07:57,140 --> 00:07:57,940
I have meetings later.

120
00:07:58,700 --> 00:07:59,940
Regarding the procedure fees,

121
00:08:00,020 --> 00:08:01,340
my secretary will contact you.

122
00:08:02,220 --> 00:08:03,380
That's all. Goodbye.

123
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:05,140
Mr. Wang!

124
00:08:06,580 --> 00:08:07,300
What happened?

125
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:10,620
Mr. Wang said
he couldn't help us anymore.

126
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:12,140
He...

127
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:13,380
Uh...

128
00:08:15,900 --> 00:08:17,300
Maybe we should let this go.

129
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:20,340
I thought it was weird

130
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:21,940
when the woman offered us help.

131
00:08:22,340 --> 00:08:24,300
There's no way
we can get a free lunch like that.

132
00:08:25,420 --> 00:08:26,540
You're ignorant.

133
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:34,220
(Mister, you can't go in.)

134
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:35,620
(Why not?)

135
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:36,220
Let go of me.

136
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:37,300
Please come down, mister.

137
00:08:37,540 --> 00:08:38,580
Please listen to me.

138
00:08:38,660 --> 00:08:40,340
Mr. Wang isn't inside.

139
00:08:40,420 --> 00:08:41,900
It's not that we're stopping you.

140
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:43,420
I just saw him go in!

141
00:08:43,580 --> 00:08:45,060
He went to attend a meeting.

142
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:46,500
He must be in this building.

143
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:47,540
Please calm down.

144
00:08:47,620 --> 00:08:48,740
Keep your voice down.

145
00:08:49,140 --> 00:08:50,060
This is an office.

146
00:08:50,140 --> 00:08:50,780
I don't want to!

147
00:08:50,820 --> 00:08:51,380
Everyone is working here.

148
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:52,220
Wang, come out.

149
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:53,220
I'm sorry, mister.

150
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:54,020
Please leave.

151
00:08:56,140 --> 00:08:57,100
What are you doing?

152
00:08:58,540 --> 00:08:59,780
Trying to use violence on me?

153
00:08:59,820 --> 00:09:00,340
Get out.

154
00:09:00,740 --> 00:09:02,260
Wang, come out!

155
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:03,900
Hey!

156
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:05,300
I know you're inside there!

157
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:06,420
Let go!

158
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:06,900
Get out!

159
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:08,140
Wang!

160
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:11,780
It has nothing to do with you.
This is just between me and Wang!

161
00:09:28,830 --> 00:09:29,700
[Zhou]

162
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:37,020
(Hello, the number you're calling
is not in service.)

163
00:09:40,650 --> 00:09:42,390
(Hello, the number you're calling...)

164
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:54,980
Why are you doing this to us?

165
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:03,060
Girl.

166
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:04,580
You're up so early.

167
00:10:05,180 --> 00:10:05,940
I get up to water the flowers.

168
00:10:07,180 --> 00:10:08,140
She's all grown up.

169
00:10:08,260 --> 00:10:08,780
She is.

170
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:09,820
We've known her since she was little.

171
00:10:09,900 --> 00:10:10,660
That's right.

172
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:13,580
She's become a mature lady now.

173
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:19,780
Hello, Yunshen.

174
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:20,780
Dr. Zhu.

175
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:23,100
I shall congratulate you
on your reinstatement.

176
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,460
Give me a second.

177
00:10:28,070 --> 00:10:29,000
[Dr. Li: Meng's parents
withdrew the lawsuit.]

178
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,000
[Come back now.
We're in the weeds here.]

179
00:10:31,580 --> 00:10:32,580
You're amazing.

180
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:33,620
How did you know about this?

181
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:35,460
Dr. Li just texted me.

182
00:10:35,540 --> 00:10:36,940
I'm faster than him.

183
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:39,220
You're a soothsayer.

184
00:10:40,140 --> 00:10:42,420
Did you help me?

185
00:10:43,060 --> 00:10:43,980
I'm not taking someone's credit.

186
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:45,460
Zhizhi helped you.

187
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:48,100
Zhizhi?

188
00:10:59,740 --> 00:11:00,420
Dr. Zhou.

189
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:03,060
Thank you so much.

190
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:04,380
Yunshen told me everything.

191
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:09,020
There's no need.

192
00:11:26,020 --> 00:11:26,860
Guess who I am.

193
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:32,380
My darling.

194
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:37,500
Let's go and grab something to eat.

195
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:47,340
Bro!

196
00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:49,940
Xizhou.

197
00:11:53,300 --> 00:11:54,220
How thoughtful of you.

198
00:11:55,460 --> 00:11:56,380
Just now,

199
00:11:56,980 --> 00:11:58,500
I got the munchies. I ate xiaolongbaos
with crab meat filling.

200
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:00,220
Sorry for the wait.

201
00:12:00,540 --> 00:12:01,340
Welcome back.

202
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:02,460
Let's go.

203
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:02,980
Come on.

204
00:12:15,570 --> 00:12:18,580
[Soft Congee]

205
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:30,820
(This plot is new.)

206
00:12:31,420 --> 00:12:33,380
(Hopefully, the real-life couple)

207
00:12:33,420 --> 00:12:34,420
(can live in forever happiness.)

208
00:12:40,940 --> 00:12:42,340
(Live in forever happiness?)

209
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:44,100
(Do you live in a feudal era?)

210
00:12:45,180 --> 00:12:46,140
(You're right.)

211
00:12:46,260 --> 00:12:47,460
(The commenter
must be from a feudal era.)

212
00:12:48,860 --> 00:12:51,140
(It's said that
the hero is a jerk in real life.)

213
00:12:51,260 --> 00:12:52,900
(The heroine is devastated.)

214
00:12:52,980 --> 00:12:55,460
(That's why she created a plot
that's the opposite of the real story.)

215
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:59,580
(So, the author
doesn't continue the comic)

216
00:13:00,140 --> 00:13:01,140
(because the heroine is being confined.)

217
00:13:01,660 --> 00:13:03,580
(This is scary.)

218
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:08,500
(A load of bull.)

219
00:13:14,620 --> 00:13:15,140
(Hey,)

220
00:13:15,540 --> 00:13:16,580
(you're insulated)

221
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:17,700
(by the feudal social values, right?)

222
00:13:24,890 --> 00:13:26,530
(Do you think you can go unpunished)

223
00:13:26,620 --> 00:13:27,540
(when you spew nonsense online?)

224
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:29,700
(Just wait.
I'll bring you out one by one.)

225
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:53,740
[Cindy of Read Comic]

226
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:54,860
(My goodness.)

227
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:56,700
(My lady.)

228
00:13:56,900 --> 00:13:58,620
(My godsend.)

229
00:13:59,060 --> 00:14:01,340
(Please! Update the comic.)

230
00:14:01,940 --> 00:14:03,660
(The editor and your followers)

231
00:14:03,740 --> 00:14:04,660
(are chewing me out.)

232
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:06,820
(Please consider the passion
of your followers,)

233
00:14:06,900 --> 00:14:08,500
(don't leave them hanging.)

234
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:20,000
[Soft Congee]

235
00:14:34,540 --> 00:14:35,860
(This plot is new!)

236
00:14:36,260 --> 00:14:38,220
(Hopefully, the real-life couple)

237
00:14:38,300 --> 00:14:39,180
(can live in forever happiness.)

238
00:14:39,180 --> 00:14:39,870
[This plot is new!]

239
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:42,220
[Hopefully, the real-life couple
can live in forever happiness.]

240
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:52,740
Boss.

241
00:14:53,540 --> 00:14:54,900
We're dining out later.

242
00:14:54,980 --> 00:14:55,580
Join us.

243
00:14:55,820 --> 00:14:56,260
No.

244
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:57,180
I'm meeting my girlfriend later.

245
00:14:58,180 --> 00:14:58,860
Boss.

246
00:14:59,420 --> 00:15:00,820
You're together every day.

247
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:01,500
Besides,

248
00:15:01,540 --> 00:15:03,180
Dr. Zhu's trouble
has already been solved.

249
00:15:03,380 --> 00:15:05,020
Don't you think
you should give us some reward?

250
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:07,220
If I leave my girlfriend aside

251
00:15:07,340 --> 00:15:08,820
and hang out with you guys,

252
00:15:08,940 --> 00:15:10,340
it makes me think that I'm dense.

253
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:12,780
Are you trying to provoke us?

254
00:15:12,980 --> 00:15:13,820
What did you say?

255
00:15:15,180 --> 00:15:15,980
I said...

256
00:15:16,180 --> 00:15:17,460
I said Dr. Zhu is beautiful.

257
00:15:20,460 --> 00:15:21,020
Boss.

258
00:15:21,660 --> 00:15:23,180
If so, we'll go without you.

259
00:15:27,220 --> 00:15:27,980
(I'm sorry)

260
00:15:28,220 --> 00:15:29,660
(for having kept you waiting.)

261
00:15:30,420 --> 00:15:31,140
(It's fine.)

262
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:32,260
(I enjoy waiting for you.)

263
00:15:37,300 --> 00:15:39,900
Are you still upset about Meng's death?

264
00:15:41,660 --> 00:15:42,340
I'm feeling better now.

265
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:44,660
Because you gave me these flowers.

266
00:15:46,620 --> 00:15:48,020
Do girls

267
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:49,140
like flowers that much?

268
00:15:50,020 --> 00:15:51,460
Yes, girls like receiving flowers.

269
00:15:51,860 --> 00:15:53,220
I parked the car over there.

270
00:15:53,420 --> 00:15:56,140
The underground garage here is full.

271
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:57,460
I'll go and get it.

272
00:15:58,700 --> 00:15:59,260
Wait for me here.

273
00:16:12,860 --> 00:16:13,780
Zhu.

274
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:17,780
Mr. Meng?

275
00:16:17,900 --> 00:16:18,980
Why are you here?

276
00:16:20,140 --> 00:16:21,540
My daughter's gone

277
00:16:21,980 --> 00:16:23,780
and yet you're dating here.

278
00:16:24,780 --> 00:16:26,340
How dare you!

279
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:28,300
What are you doing?

280
00:16:28,420 --> 00:16:28,940
Come with me!

281
00:16:31,460 --> 00:16:32,140
Let go!

282
00:16:36,540 --> 00:16:37,260
What's wrong with you?

283
00:16:44,660 --> 00:16:45,540
Stop it!

284
00:16:49,140 --> 00:16:49,980
Get off me!

285
00:16:55,780 --> 00:16:56,460
Let go of him!

286
00:17:10,340 --> 00:17:10,940
