00:35:54,020 --> 00:35:56,300
that you fooled me before.

574
00:35:57,340 --> 00:35:59,300
Every company gathered

575
00:36:00,780 --> 00:36:03,820
to come up with solutions

576
00:36:03,940 --> 00:36:04,980
when something happened.

577
00:36:05,580 --> 00:36:06,940
However, Mr. Fu

578
00:36:07,460 --> 00:36:08,580
is really intriguing.

579
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:09,780
He cooped himself at home.

580
00:36:09,900 --> 00:36:12,580
Besides, he had the court

581
00:36:13,140 --> 00:36:15,500
to send me a summons to tackle me.

582
00:36:16,380 --> 00:36:19,060
- No.
- Apparently, he wanted to corner you

583
00:36:19,140 --> 00:36:20,620
and make me his scapegoat?

584
00:36:20,740 --> 00:36:21,380
Mr. Cheng.

585
00:36:22,100 --> 00:36:23,780
I have no idea what he's up to.

586
00:36:23,980 --> 00:36:25,180
I've left Lingtian.

587
00:36:25,740 --> 00:36:26,340
Fine.

588
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:27,660
I don't want to make things difficult
for you.

589
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:29,380
As long as you took the half
of the claim.

590
00:36:29,540 --> 00:36:29,980
No.

591
00:36:30,180 --> 00:36:31,340
Are you kidding me?

592
00:36:31,580 --> 00:36:32,900
I don't have the money.

593
00:36:33,060 --> 00:36:35,660
You can seek your aunt, Jiang Shuning.

594
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:37,260
She can back you up, right?

595
00:36:37,540 --> 00:36:39,420
Go and convince her

596
00:36:39,620 --> 00:36:41,580
like how you convinced me then.

597
00:36:41,740 --> 00:36:43,540
Perhaps I can write an IOU first.

598
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:44,740
Consider that I owe you.

599
00:36:45,060 --> 00:36:46,220
I'll pay you back slowly.

600
00:36:47,740 --> 00:36:48,860
Pay me back slowly?

601
00:36:51,180 --> 00:36:51,900
Are you planning

602
00:36:51,980 --> 00:36:53,660
to pay me back after I die?

603
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:55,340
Don't you worry.

604
00:36:55,500 --> 00:36:57,420
I'll bring you along before my death.

605
00:36:58,260 --> 00:36:58,780
By the way,

606
00:36:59,060 --> 00:37:00,740
your wife, who works as a model,
as well.

607
00:37:02,900 --> 00:37:04,380
You told me

608
00:37:04,700 --> 00:37:06,100
that she's pregnant, right?

609
00:37:06,220 --> 00:37:07,300
I'm telling you,

610
00:37:07,420 --> 00:37:08,260
don't do anything ridiculous.

611
00:37:08,340 --> 00:37:09,220
If you dare harm her,

612
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:10,580
I won't let you off! I'm telling you!

613
00:37:10,580 --> 00:37:11,500
Very good!

614
00:37:11,700 --> 00:37:13,220
As long as you feel threatened.

615
00:37:16,580 --> 00:37:17,100
Go!

616
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:11,820
You're awake?

617
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:15,940
Why are you

618
00:38:17,020 --> 00:38:18,140
in this uniform?

619
00:38:20,540 --> 00:38:21,780
I used my wit

620
00:38:22,020 --> 00:38:23,100
to get in here.

621
00:38:33,610 --> 00:38:35,090
Stay still.

622
00:38:46,620 --> 00:38:47,420
Fu Yunshen.

623
00:38:48,220 --> 00:38:50,180
You're not a formidable wall.

624
00:38:50,340 --> 00:38:51,700
Why did you do that?

625
00:38:57,780 --> 00:38:59,540
My injury isn't fatal.

626
00:39:02,060 --> 00:39:03,020
Don't worry.

627
00:39:06,260 --> 00:39:07,140
I'm sorry.

628
00:39:08,620 --> 00:39:09,900
You're injured

629
00:39:11,820 --> 00:39:13,700
because of me.

630
00:39:16,420 --> 00:39:17,700
Don't blame yourself.

631
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:20,220
I would save anyone

632
00:39:20,820 --> 00:39:21,820
who's in danger

633
00:39:21,940 --> 00:39:23,380
when I see them on some random street.

634
00:39:24,580 --> 00:39:25,500
Besides,

635
00:39:28,140 --> 00:39:29,700
you're my girlfriend.

636
00:39:34,860 --> 00:39:36,140
Does it hurt?

637
00:39:39,380 --> 00:39:40,100
Yes, very much so.

638
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:42,260
Well, what do I do now?

639
00:39:55,380 --> 00:39:56,260
Are you not coming over?

640
00:40:06,180 --> 00:40:09,540
I don't feel any pain now.

641
00:40:09,940 --> 00:40:10,740
Really?

642
00:40:18,740 --> 00:40:19,980
The IV drip kit is prepared.

643
00:40:20,140 --> 00:40:21,500
Why are you still here?

644
00:40:23,140 --> 00:40:24,420
Who let you in?

645
00:40:25,620 --> 00:40:27,100
We're wondering

646
00:40:27,140 --> 00:40:28,060
what took her so long.

647
00:40:28,780 --> 00:40:30,260
Can't you see I'm watching drama?

648
00:40:33,700 --> 00:40:34,820
Do you want to join me?

649
00:40:36,220 --> 00:40:37,140
No.

650
00:40:38,020 --> 00:40:38,980
Leave the room, then.

651
00:40:46,220 --> 00:40:47,460
That was scary.

652
00:40:52,940 --> 00:40:54,580
Put your arm down.

653
00:40:55,740 --> 00:40:56,420
Okay.

654
00:41:02,300 --> 00:41:02,980
Yunshen.

655
00:41:04,660 --> 00:41:06,020
Don't you think

656
00:41:06,300 --> 00:41:07,660
we're having

657
00:41:07,900 --> 00:41:09,380
a secret date here?

658
00:41:11,820 --> 00:41:12,900
What nonsense

659
00:41:12,940 --> 00:41:14,820
are you thinking about, huh?

660
00:41:16,420 --> 00:41:17,340
Nothing.

661
00:41:19,020 --> 00:41:20,220
Secret date my foot.

662
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:23,420
Does it hurt?

663
00:41:52,740 --> 00:41:56,340
♪I see you in a dark corner♪

664
00:41:56,620 --> 00:41:59,980
♪With vulnerability overwhelming you♪

665
00:42:00,220 --> 00:42:02,300
♪Biting your lips
and facing away from me♪

666
00:42:02,540 --> 00:42:06,540
♪You break the walls of stubbornness♪

667
00:42:07,380 --> 00:42:10,340
♪Once more, another sundown
swiftly passes by♪

668
00:42:10,620 --> 00:42:15,780
♪Love is like a lie at the end
of the century♪

669
00:42:15,940 --> 00:42:21,700
♪That almost fools me♪

670
00:42:31,580 --> 00:42:38,180
♪A kiss can heal this wrecked world♪

671
00:42:38,500 --> 00:42:45,140
♪If there is a slight possibility
of avoiding loneliness♪

672
00:42:45,420 --> 00:42:51,820
♪Let me endure the heavy rainfall
with you♪

673
00:42:52,100 --> 00:42:56,140
♪If there is a slight possibility♪

674
00:42:56,380 --> 00:43:02,260
♪The moon that once shone for me
should stay radiate♪

675
00:43:02,580 --> 00:43:08,380
♪You'll regain happiness
when you are true to yourself♪

676
00:43:17,860 --> 00:43:24,820
♪You feel my pain♪

677
00:43:24,940 --> 00:43:31,900
♪No reason for those meaningless winds
to pass by me♪

678
00:43:32,140 --> 00:43:38,820
♪When the meaningless things hit me♪

679
00:43:46,700 --> 00:43:53,180
♪Why must we miss out on each other
when our hearts are broken?♪

680
00:43:53,900 --> 00:44:00,500
♪Imitating others who flinch and escape
after love sparks fade away♪

681
00:44:00,660 --> 00:44:09,500
♪All I yearn for
is the warmth deep within you♪
